---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Portafolio | David Guevara">
	
	<section class="flex flex-col gap-8 pb-10 pt-10 items-start justify-center min-h-[70vh]">
		
		<div class="animate-fade-in-down">
			<img 
				src="/perfil.jpg" 
				alt="Foto de perfil" 
				class="w-32 h-32 rounded-full border-4 border-cyan-400/50 object-cover shadow-[0_0_30px_rgba(34,211,238,0.2)] hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300"
			/>
		</div>

		<div class="animate-fade-in-down delay-100">
			<span class="text-cyan-400 text-xs md:text-sm tracking-widest border border-cyan-400/30 px-3 py-1 rounded bg-cyan-400/5 shadow-[0_0_10px_rgba(34,211,238,0.2)]">
				● SYSTEM_ONLINE
			</span>
		</div>

		<h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-bold text-white leading-tight">
			Hola, soy <br />
			<span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-400 to-purple-600 animate-pulse-slow">
				David Guevara
			</span>
		</h1>

		<p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-gray-400 max-w-2xl border-l-2 border-purple-500/50 pl-4 font-mono">
			&lt;Desarrollador Web /&gt; apasionado por crear interfaces dinámicas y eficientes. 
			Especializado en <strong>Vue.js</strong> y <strong>Astro</strong>, usando Inteligencia Artificial para optimizar el flujo de desarrollo.
		</p>

		<div class="mt-8 p-4 md:p-6 border border-white/10 rounded-lg bg-black/40 backdrop-blur-md w-full max-w-lg shadow-2xl">
			<div class="flex gap-2 mb-4 border-b border-white/5 pb-2">
				<div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-red-500/50"></div>
				<div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-yellow-500/50"></div>
				<div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-green-500/50"></div>
			</div>
			<div class="font-mono text-sm space-y-2">
				<p class="text-gray-500">Last login: Today from 127.0.0.1</p>
				<p class="text-purple-400">➜  ~ <span class="text-gray-300">init portfolio --dev</span></p>
				<p class="text-gray-400">> Cargando proyectos...</p>
				<p class="text-gray-400">> Integrando IA...</p>
				<p class="text-green-400">> Hecho. Stack listo para desplegar.</p>
				<p class="text-purple-400 animate-pulse">➜  ~ <span class="w-2 h-4 bg-gray-500 inline-block align-middle ml-1"></span></p>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 mt-4">
			<a href="/proyectos" class="group relative px-6 py-3 font-bold text-black bg-white overflow-hidden rounded transition-all hover:bg-cyan-400 hover:text-white hover:scale-105 active:scale-95 font-mono">
				Ver Proyectos
				<span class="absolute right-2 top-2 w-2 h-2 bg-black/20 rounded-full group-hover:bg-white/50"></span>
			</a>
			<a href="/contacto" class="px-6 py-3 border border-white/20 text-white rounded hover:bg-white/10 transition-colors hover:border-cyan-400/50 font-mono">
				Contactar_
			</a>
		</div>

	</section>

</Layout>